Pages: 41-46
Author-Name: Rosalie L Tung
Author-Workplace-Name: Faculty of Business, Simon Fraser University, Burnaby, Canada
File-URL: http://www.palgrave-journals.com/jibs/journal/v39/n1/pdf/8400331a.pdf
File-Format: Application/pdf
